~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Author: Chris Arriola
Date:   Dec. 7, 2010
Description: This program provides a measure of readability -- how good a
    reader needs to be in order to understand a passage of English text.
    This is based on the article from http://www.readability.info/info.shtml
    and from CIT591.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Running:

- Compile the Readability.scala file by 'scala Readability.scala'
- Run the program by using: 'scala Readability'
- After selecting a file, the measures will be outputed.

